A very refreshing salad with an exciting dressing. I found the onion quite overpowering (although I did use the wrong kind!) so made it a second time without, and it was wonderful. I also put in grated orange peel which seemed to enhance the 'oranginess' I also didn't have any fresh mint, ... I am curious to try it with that! I will be making this salad a lot!

